      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "War on Jap and Chinese house\nservants in Spokane has been de-\nclared by the Card and Label\nleague, affiliated with the Central\nTrades council.\n\n\nThe label league agrees to get a\nsatisfactory white servant, male or\nfemale, to replace any Asiatic EN-.\nployed in domestic work in Spo-\nkane, If the family having such\nhelp will make application to it.\n\n\nA meeting of the Card and Label\nleague will be held next Tuesday\nevening at the Cooks hall on How\nard street."
